WEBVTT

00:00.300 --> 00:03.040
I saw an accident on my way home today.

00:03.420 --> 00:08.820
Something fell at a construction site and someone died.

00:09.420 --> 00:13.240
Cop cars and ambulances were everywhere, and lots of people, too.

00:13.240 --> 00:17.260
It’s sad that someone died.

00:18.200 --> 00:21.260
I wouldn’t want something like that to happen to me all of a sudden.

00:22.060 --> 00:24.540
I am...
